### Register a student
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "John Doe",
  "password": "secret123",
  "user_type": "student",
  "student_id": "STU001",
  "class_level": "300L",
  "emergency_contact": "Jane Doe",
  "emergency_phone": "08012345678"
}

### Register a staff
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "Dr Smith",
  "password": "secret123",
  "user_type": "staff",
  "staff_id": "STF001",
  "staff_type": "counselor"
}

### Login as student (just the ID, no email)
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=STU001&password=secret123

### Login as staff
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded`    

username=STF001&password=secret123